  "remarks": "Qdi.081\nPassport no.: 00085243 issued in Sanaa, Yemen, issued on 17 Nov. 1997. \nArrested in Karachi, Pakistan, 30 Sep. 2002. In custody of the United States of America, as of May 2010.\nReview pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 25 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 30 September 2002 (amended on 26 November 2004, 25 July 2006, 2 July 2007, 27 Jul 2007 and 23 Dec. 2010, 6 Dec 2019).",
